commit.message: Dropped usage of utlz.flo() and went Python 3
Full functionality of both scripts and library

Made verify_scts.py work.
Also verify_scts.py --latest-logs will work
Minor: Added word "debug" into debug output

Modernized version of ctutlz.
There is TLS 1.2 -connectivity, but futher work is still needed.
Add support for servers configured with SNI
in case of scts-by-cert also try to verify scts against every cert of the chain of the tls handshake (could be disordered)
refactor test_verify_signature() and add test data
download new versions of log lists into test-data dir
fabric task uplogs now downloads both json log lists

Refactoring of _determine_latest_pythons()

Split into extract_minors_from_setup_py() and determine_latest_pythons()
and move them along with highest_minor() to module fabsetup.fabutils.
update parsing of changed known-logs.html webpage
